    "description": "<strong>游戏简介</strong><br>《FUEL &amp; FURY》是一款激烈的俯视角射击和驾驶游戏，你将驾驶死亡机器般的汽车或使用各种疯狂武器来横扫敌群！从香蕉炮到骨头粉碎机，你拥有所有制造混乱的工具。在穿越被感染的乡村时，与僵尸、土匪和军队展开对抗！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206420/extras/f36766f4ba4df597eb2da7cb79981a7e.poster.avif?t=1730274047\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206420/extras/f36766f4ba4df597eb2da7cb79981a7e.webm?t=1730274047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206420/extras/f36766f4ba4df597eb2da7cb79981a7e.mp4?t=1730274047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>故事背景</strong><br>作为玩家的你必须在残酷的冬天来临之前逃离这个国家。但要当心！军队另有打算。他们试图控制感染，这意味着要阻止像你这样的人逃走...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206420/extras/ea0b92cf5d753a2e27b53d926e54c0f8.poster.avif?t=1730274047\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206420/extras/ea0b92cf5d753a2e27b53d926e54c0f8.webm?t=1730274047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206420/extras/ea0b92cf5d753a2e27b53d926e54c0f8.mp4?t=1730274047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏玩法</strong><br>从一辆普通汽车开始，将其改造成你最致命的朋友！寻找升级部件，安装炮塔、尖刺、强力引擎等。但你的汽车不是唯一的僵尸杀手 - 你自己也是！利用各种武器和物品创造疯狂的搭配和协同效应。<br><br>当然，你需要有目标来使用这些火力：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>碾压饥渴脑髓的感染者大军<br></li><li>躲避拥有恶毒技能的特殊僵尸<br></li><li>智胜寻找容易下手目标的匪帮<br></li><li>在接近自由的路上与全副武装的士兵正面交锋</li></ul><br>你探索的每个区域都充满危险，别忘了还有等着真正考验你实力的致命Boss！<br><br>控制很简单 - 驾驶、闪避、射击和生存 - 但掌握这些技能是在这个不死噩梦中存活的关键。每次死亡都是一次教训，重生比僵尸咬人还快，让你始终保持在行动中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206420/extras/7155e6213e97887aa320ba87bb10197b.poster.avif?t=1730274047\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206420/extras/7155e6213e97887aa320ba87bb10197b.webm?t=1730274047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206420/extras/7155e6213e97887aa320ba87bb10197b.mp4?t=1730274047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>就是这样。深呼吸。你能行的。<br><br><strong>你会成为在新的不死时代中幸存下来的人吗？如果是，那就现在加入愿望单，准备开始你人生中最刺激的驾驶吧！！！</strong>",
